Usage:

  ArxLibertatisLightingCalculator.exe [options]

Options:

  --level             Name of the level, e.g. "level1". Use together with
                      arx-data-dir

  --arx-data-dir      Path to the arx data dir, so we can find the level by
                      name. The one containing the folders editor, game,
                      graph, localisation and misc. Required if using the
                      level option

  --dlf               The path to the dlf file, requires fts and llf

  --fts               The path to the fts file, requires dlf and llf

  --llf               The path to the llf file, requires fts and dlf

  --lighting-profile  What lighting profile to use. Possible Values:
                      Distance, Danae, DistanceAngle, DistanceAngleShadow